desc_short	-----								Prismatica is a colorful puzzle game with a brand new twist inspired by Rubik’s Cubes, Sudoku, Dodecahedrons and way too much caffeine. Prismatica's simple gameplay and deceptively challenging puzzles will tickle the brains of both beginners and veterans alike.							
